---

## My Approach

<ul style="margin-top:8px;">
<li>✔️ 15 years’ experience with puppies through seniors (including anxious dogs)</li>
<li>✔️ Walks tailored to age and energy — even on rainy days!</li>
<li>✔️ Small numbers only — quality over quantity</li>
<li>✔️ Honest, regular updates (photos, messages, progress notes)</li>
<li>✔️ First-aid aware and fully insured with Petplan</li>
</ul>

---

## Home Setup

<p>
I live in a relaxed, calm home with a secure garden and plenty of space for play and downtime.  
If your dog has specific needs — medication, crate training, recall work, or feeding routines — I’ll always follow your plan so they feel safe and understood.
</p>


